{"tid":1022804,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"媽咪患上左急性思覺失調，我真係唔知點算","createTime":"2019-02-15T09:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T15:47:12.000Z","uid":17667,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"6d6ce90e6688b27b688b716ff67b4d4e94e3d67e","tid":1022804,"uid":17667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:27:30.000Z","msg":"好傷心，覺得媽咪真係好可憐..<br />\n我真係唔知點樣面對呢件事..<br />\n而家佢係醫院，我就自己係屋企。<br />\n身邊既人有安慰我，叫我唔好亂諗，但我諗起佢發作嗰個樣我就忍唔住喊..<br />\n我返工都返唔到，請左幾日假..<br />\n醫生話佢個情況需要時間去治療，但又講唔到其實係要幾耐。<br />\n我好驚自己會頂唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我亦都唔敢向身邊人再放負，驚佢地會嫌我煩，唔會再理我，甚至離開我..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我好想好想佢好返，真係好想。<br />\n我好愛我媽咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f379c8c811bd52f2b71c9d69fd710ebd1e81ff66","tid":1022804,"uid":189646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:29:33.000Z","msg":"有咩病徵同行為異常？"},{"pid":"5f6ca78d80748cb542eed28fffc891af1c1ad2a1","tid":1022804,"uid":26429,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:32:03.000Z","msg":"思覺失調原來都有急性<br />\n即係突然痴左線？<br />\n樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6dd80880c2d185ce3b2aa6b4590cfd489f62d3","tid":1022804,"uid":30615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:32:36.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43558a7a7ecd06df4ab6b3f3987ff7f49a608e43","tid":1022804,"uid":228663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:34:36.000Z","msg":"樓主加油,我相信呢度應該有好多人同我一樣願意聽你放負"},{"pid":"74e9fc4443b4b9653769280259d1fe6dc8abc6b6","tid":1022804,"uid":129900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:35:08.000Z","msg":"有藥食架喎."},{"pid":"50c3f5d37defca9043cb31f5514ddd0bd57cee